    = link_to edit_content_path, class: 'inline-flex items-center rounded border border-gray-300 bg-white px-2.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-gray-700 shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:ring-offset-2' do
      div 編集


